    #impress
      #automate.step.slide{"data-x" => "-1000", "data-y" => "-1500"}
        %q
          Test Automation
          %br/
          %br/
          %b Jasdeep Madan
          <br>
          %b ThoughtWorks
          <input type=button id=moveNext />
      .step.slide{"data-x" => "0", "data-y" => "-1500"}
        %q
          %strong Test Automation you ask?
      .step.slide{"data-x" => "1000", "data-y" => "-1500"}
        %small
          %p
          %br/
          %br/
          Testing is organized skepticism. Itâ€™s the belief that things may not be as they seem; that things could be different.
